thread.title: Sallie Ketteringham

author: Sallie Ketteringham
title: Sallie Ketteringham
text: Good service at booking over the phone but at the airport (Thrifty) after arriving unexpectedly late at the return office (due to delays on the road) I could not fill the car as I almost missed my flight out. The extra charge of $3.30 per litre is very high. I expected to pay a slight excess but that much is exorbitant. The car was a late model Corolla and very good to drive.
